          'description' => 'Associative object mapping topic names to arrays of keywords. E.g. {"tech":["software","AI","cloud"],"policy":["law","regulation","government"]}. Default: built-in topics (tech, science, business, policy, security).',
        ),
      ),
      'required' => 
